body_html: This question is better asked on StackOverflow since it is not a bug or feature request. There is also a larger community that reads questions there. In particular, we do not intend the documentation at master to describe the differences with previous versions of TensorFlow `contrib. Thanks!

body: This question is better asked on  [StackOverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/tensorflow) since it is not a  bug or feature request.
